<h2 class="text-uppercase">3Lines Unbound</h2>
<p>3Lines is a Denver based Venture Capital firm laser-focused on investing in early stage technology companies. Very often, our Limited Partners and the Entrepreneurs ask us- what are the three lines in 3Lines? <b>We say, ‘Ah, it’s like 1,2,3. Time, Capital and Growth, these are the three lines. Or, said differently, it’s the S-curve of the venture capital world! At the bottom of an S-curve it feels like not much is happening at all. Once a startup crosses an inflection point, suddenly capital investment starts growing wild.</b> We raise capital from our limited partners and we scout, screen and invest that capital in carefully culled and curated startup companies. Over time, we help grow those startup companies with the help from our network of no less than technology gurus, the brain heavyweights, the folks who know Software, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, IoT, CyberSecurity, Blockchain, Software Defined Networking and Enterprise Applications ! 
</p>

