<p>We invest largely in the US across growth oriented select industries but also keep our sight on India as well where we do not want to miss out on a rapidly growing startup ecosystem and where, for example, the number of unicorns has gone up to 24 from just 1 in a short span of six years! We have built a portfolio of 17 early stage companies with a projected MOM of of 2X.</p>

<p>When we talk about winning and success, we are very clear. We speak of three major factors, the three T’s- the Team, the Thesis and the Traction. We have built a strong team of General Partners and the Deal Screening Council; we are vectored along a unique investment thesis and, with our very first exit in just over eighteen months of investment, 3Lines has begun to ‘tread with traction’ as well! 
</p>

